CREDITS**: Thanks to ashiie for helping me get this map done. Also help testing it, for ideas, and the 

support. Plus for likeing these two colors for me to use. =) thx ashley, <3.

INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS**: Install: Copy the map (bsp file) and paste it into your Cstrike maps directory.
\Steam\SteamApps\Name\counter-strike source\cstrike\map


INSTALLATION TEXTURES"materials" INSTRUCTIONS**: Copy the aim_pinkalicious folder and paste it into your 

\SteamApps\username\counter-strike source\cstrike\materials\aim_pinkalicious


DESCRIPTION**: A remake of the aim orange textures, into pink.

BUGS: The top of the water is messed up, but the inside and when u look out of the water "when you're in the 

water look to the top its prefect. Just the top of it when looking at the water. If you have any idea on how 

to fix just email me or leave a pm message on my fpsbanana account.

COMMENTS: If you like pink and blue this is your map.
